text: "Na-NaNa-Na" is a 2005 rap song by American rapper Nelly. The song featured American singer Jazze Pha. It was the third and prev_title from his third studio album Sweat. The song was released in 2005 in the United States. The song reached #65 on the U.S. Billboard Hot R&B;/Hip-Hop Songs. Category:Nelly songs Category:2005 songs
